comments: Melton (PHI) is not in a legal guarding position alongside Mathurin (IND) when he makes contact with his body, which alters his driving shot attempt.
Harrell (PHI) slightly extends his arm and marginal contact occurs with Nembhard (IND) as he engages on the pick.
Harden (PHI) brings his arm toward Haliburton's (IND) path and marginal contact occurs during Haliburton's drive.
Harrell (PHI) establishes himself in Nembhard's (IND) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Melton (PHI) initiates the contact with Haliburton (IND) and dislodges him from his legally obtained position off-ball.
Harden (PHI) is moving alongside Haliburton's (IND) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Harden (PHI) reaches for the ball and marginal contact occurs with Haliburton's (IND) arm as he makes his intended pass to Turner (IND).
Harrell (PHI) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
Harrell (PHI) establishes himself in Nembhard's (IND) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Harden (PHI) stops his forward momentum as he goes to, not through, Turner's (IND) space and marginal contact occurs as Harden releases away during the drive.
Turner (IND) legally contests Maxey's (PHI) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Nembhard (IND) and Harrell (PHI) mutually engage and disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Maxey (PHI) makes clean contact with the ball and deflects it away from Haliburton (IND).
Harden (PHI) is moving alongside Haliburton's (IND) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together on the perimeter.
Harden (PHI) initiates contact with Haliburton's (IND) arm, which causes Haliburton to lose control of the ball at the end of the drive.
Turner (IND) jumps alongside Maxey's (PHI) path during his contest and he then makes contact with Maxey's lower body which affects his ability to complete the shot.
Harris (PHI) extends his forearm and dislodges Hield (IND) from his rebounding position.
Harrell (PHI) legally contests the shot attempt and avoids making contact with Hield's (IND) head.
Turner (IND) moves slightly laterally into Maxey's (PHI) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Nembhard (IND) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Haliburton (IND) slightly extends his hand and marginal contact occurs with Maxey's (PHI) body during his driving shot attempt.
Maxey (PHI) lands in front of Nembhard (IND) and the marginal contact does not dislodge him from his defensive position.
Hield (IND) brushes Harrell's (PHI) arm and marginal contact occurs during Harrell's dunk attempt.
Harden (PHI) makes contact with the ball before his hand slides off and marginal contact occurs as he brushes Mathurin's (IND) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Harrell (PHI) makes clean contact with the ball to block Mathurin's (IND) driving shot attempt. Any follow-through body contact after the block is deemed incidental.
Mathurin (IND) initiates contact with Harden's (PHI) arm, which affects Harden's SQBR.
Turner (IND) extends his arm and initiates contact with Maxey's (PHI) body while he is airborne, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Harrell (PHI) makes contact with the ball while it is still in the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
Melton (PHI) moves alongside Haliburton's (IND) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the driving shot attempt.
Harden (PHI) briefly rests his forearm on Mathurin's (IND) body and marginal contact occurs as he releases away without extending it at the end of the drive.
Mathurin (IND) jumps toward Harden (PHI) on his contest and initiates contact with Harden's lower body, affecting the jump shot attempt.
Turner (IND) establishes himself in Melton's (PHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Harden (PHI) jumps alongside Mathurin (IND) while resting a hand on his body and does not apply force as he makes clean ball contact to block the shot at the basket.
Nembhard (IND) commits a take foul on Harris (PHI).
Harden (PHI) and Mathurin (IND) mutually engage and disengage and marginal contact occurs during the inbound.
Turner (IND) establishes himself in Thybulle's (PHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Harden (PHI) commits a take foul on Mathurin (IND) prior to his upward shooting motion. A personal foul is correctly assessed.
Thybulle (PHI) and Mathurin (IND) briefly engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs during the inbound.
Harden (PHI) moves into and makes contact with Hield's (IND) body, which affects Hield's jump shot attempt.
